    "summary": "The user is pressuring an AI assistant to locate a missing medical supply shipment (#998) to avoid filing a formal claim. The assistant repeatedly requests a tracking number, eventually stating it lacks direct access to proprietary logistics systems and offers to escalate the matter to a human department.",
